<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>文件排序（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>filesort</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）是通过相应的排序算法，将取得的数据在内存中进行排序。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>M</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>y</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>会给每个线程分配分配一块内存用于排序，称为</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort_buffer</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，可以通过</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort_buffer_size
     </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>参数来手动设置</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort buffer</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的大小</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#2E75B5'>SHOW VARIABLES LIKE </span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#70AD47'>'%sort_buffer_size%' </span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#BFBFBF'>-- 262144</span><span
style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";color:#BFBFBF'>字节</span><span
style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";color:#BFBFBF'> 256KB</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:1.125in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
font-size:12.0pt;color:#BFBFBF'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>SET GLOBAL </span><span
lang=zh-CN>sort_buffer_size = 1024</span><span style='color:#ED7D31'

lang=en-US><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span><span
style='color:#BFBFBF' lang=zh-CN>--</span><span style='color:#BFBFBF'
lang=en-US> 1M</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>mysql </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>需要将数据在内存中进行排序，所使用的内存区域是通过</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> sort_buffer_size </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>系统变量所设置的排序区。这个排序区是每个线程独享的，所以说可能在同一时刻在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>MySQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>中可能存在多个</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'> sort buffer </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>内存区域。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>如果当</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort
     buffer</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>空间无法容纳我们需要排序的数据时，就需要在磁盘创建临时文件存放排序数据。临时文件排序采用归并排序的算法，首先会把需要排序的数据拆分到多个临时文件里同步进行排序操作，然后把多个排好序的文件合并成一个结果集返回，因此这时排序速度会慢很多。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>为了避免使用临时文件排序，在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> M</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>y</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>SQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中会通过系统参数</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>
     max_length_for_sort_data </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的大小（默认</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>1024</span><span style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>），和查询语句所需取出的字段大小的总和进行比较，来切换排序算法来对排序进行优化。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt;color:#70AD47'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=en-US>SHOW VARIABLES LIKE</span><span
style='color:#181818' lang=zh-CN><span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span></span><span
style='color:#70AD47' lang=zh-CN>'max_length_for_sort_data'</span><span
style='color:#181818' lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>文件排序（</span><span

     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）主要有两种排序模式：</span></li>
</ul>

  </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI"'>排序</span></p>
  </td>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt'>全字段排序</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>效率更快，避免了二次读取数据，把随机</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>IO</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>变成了顺序</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>IO</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'>，但是同时会使用更多的空间。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>默认情况下，文件排序（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>filesort</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）优先使用更快的全字段排序，即直接将查询所需的字段全部读取到</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort_buffer</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中，</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:11.5pt' lang=zh-CN>然后在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:11.5pt' lang=zh-CN> sort
     buffer </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:
     11.5pt' lang=zh-CN>中进行排序后返回结果。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=501 height=272></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>当</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>
     max_length_for_sort_data </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>大小不足时，会使用</span><span style='font-family:
     "Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>rowid </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>排序，取出</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>id</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>和排序字段，放入到</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort_buffer</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>中，然后排序，排序后需要回表再次查询，然后返回结果集。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in'><img
src="data:image/png;base64,"
width=494 height=265></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>如果想优化文件排序（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>filesort</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>）的速度，可以适当调整</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>
     max_length_for_sort_data </span><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>参数的大小。</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<p style='margin-left:.75in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'><span style='color:#2E75B5' lang=zh-CN>SET</span><span lang=zh-CN>
max_length_for_sort_data = </span><span lang=en-US>1024</span><span lang=zh-CN>;</span></p>

<p style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'><span
style='font-weight:bold'>注</span></p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>在</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> MySQL </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>8.0.20</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>之后</span><span
     style='font-weight:bold;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=en-US> </span><a
     href="https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/order-by-optimization.html#:~:text=max_length_for_sort_data%20is%20deprecated%20due%20to%20optimizer%20changes%20that%20make%20it%20obsolete%20and%20of%20no%20effect."><span
     style='font-weight:bold;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>max_length_for_sort_data</span><span style='font-weight:bold;
     font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-weight:bold;font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt'
     lang=zh-CN>已被弃用</span></a><span style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";
     font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>，即使参数仍然能够修改，但是在新的优化器中，根据数据大小和其他因素动态选择排序算法更为有效。因此优化排序应该增加</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>sort_buffer_size</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US> </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>参数的大小。理想情况下，该值应该足够大，以使整个结果集能够放入排序缓冲区</span></li>
</ul>

<p style='margin-left:.375in;font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:
12.0pt'>&nbsp;</p>

<ul type=disc style='direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;
 margin-bottom:0in'>
 <li style='margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle'><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>当表中数据量非常大时，更推荐的做法是避免使用文件排序（</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=en-US>filesort</span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>），给</span><span
     style='font-family:"Comic Sans MS";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN> order by </span><span
     style='font-family:"Microsoft YaHei UI";font-size:12.0pt' lang=zh-CN>的排序字段加索引，利用有序索引排序。</span></li>
</ul>
